flowRoot.flowPara: Young people play games for fun, for having a meeting with friends over Teamspeak/Mumble (maybe mainly to discuss about Computer Science Stuff)
But there are also situations where the game or additional software tells them that if they win the game they would win things like women, money, degree... this wishes then maybe never become true
Later the people who added these features would tell that because of this headshot or nemesis pin with knife a real person died (dt1 card) so better focus on the Computer Science stuff.
